WEBVTT

00:00:07.646 --> 00:00:09.840
Oh, excuse me!

00:00:10.642 --> 00:00:13.394
Have you ever yawned
because somebody else yawned?

00:00:13.418 --> 00:00:15.144
You aren't especially tired,

00:00:15.168 --> 00:00:18.185
yet suddenly your mouth opens wide

00:00:18.209 --> 00:00:21.211
and a big yawn

00:00:22.475 --> 00:00:23.479
comes out.

00:00:24.305 --> 00:00:27.213
This phenomenon is known
as contagious yawning.

00:00:27.237 --> 00:00:29.571
And while scientists still
don't fully understand

00:00:29.595 --> 00:00:30.615
why it happens,